  "title": "Principal Consultant",
  "description": "<ul><li><li>Must have 15+ years of IT experience in the Banking Software industry, specializing in Corporate Banking-Trade Finance and Finance Supply Chain.</li><li>Should have hands on experience in design and development of API's, Microservices in containerized, Cloud Native (Openshift) platform.</li><li>Extensive experience in Java, Springboot, ReactJS, ServiceNow, Maven, SonarQube, Cucumber.</li><li>Must have hands on experience in Kofax Total Agility tool, YAML and Kafka.</li><li>Hands on experience on automation (CI/CD) of production and staging environment to increase productivity.</li><li>Hands on experience on UI development using JavaScript frameworks such as ReactJs.</li><li>Extensive experience in data modelling, design and writing optimize SQL queries and Stored procedures.</li></li></ul>",
